{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FmqjNRa8DGzh51kkVTD2Pe","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n**Summary of implementation:**\n\n**Created files:**\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/lib/ink-workflow.tsx` — `WorkflowGraph` component with `TaskNode` helper, loop block rendering, status indicators (dim/cyan+diamond/green+check/red+cross), separator lines\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/lib/__tests__/ink-workflow.test.tsx` — 9 tests covering sequential flow, loop blocks, all 4 status states, empty flow, empty taskStates, mixed flow\n\n**Modified files:**\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/lib/ink-components.tsx` — Added `TaskNodeState` type, `FlowStep` import, extended `RendererState` with `workflowFlow`, `currentTaskName`, `taskStates`\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/lib/ink-app.tsx` — Imported `WorkflowGraph`, inserted between `Header` and `StoryBreakdown`\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/lib/ink-renderer.tsx` — Added `updateWorkflowState()` to `RendererHandle` interface, implemented it, added to `noopHandle`, initialized new state fields, re-exported `TaskNodeState`\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/lib/__tests__/ink-renderer.test.tsx` — Updated `makeState` helper with new required fields\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/14-1-workflowgraph-component.md` — Status changed to `review`, all tasks marked complete\n\n**Build:** zero TypeScript errors. **Tests:** 169 files, 4554 tests, all passing.\n\n## Session Issues\n\n- **Loop iteration counting is a heuristic.** The `loopIteration()` function in `ink-workflow.tsx` uses a simple heuristic (returns 0 or 1) because the actual iteration count must come from the workflow engine. Multi-iteration tracking requires engine-provided data that will be wired in the engine integration story. This is a known limitation documented in 